.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, nectarine, orange, pineapple
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, musician, pilot, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, indie, jazz
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, azalea, iris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, adventure, documentary, fantasy
 1. the person who growspoppy is the fan of house##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the architect##3
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 7. the teacher is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating orange is the fan of indie##1
11. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the right of the pilot##1
13. the person who growsazalea is the person eating pineapple##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | orange | nectarine | mango     | pineapple |
| Job           | pilot  | teacher   | architect | musician  |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | jazz      | house     | country   |
| Flower         | iris | orchid  | poppy   | azalea    |
| Movie-Genre     | documentary | adventure    | fantasy     | family |

