.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, blood-red, emerald, ivory
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, project-manager, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, rock, trance
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, turkish, indian
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the fan of rock is the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 4. the fan of trance is between the spanish and the turkish##2
 5. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 6. the turkish is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the mexican##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
10. the librarian is on the left of the bartender##1
11. the scientist is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes mauve is the scientist##1
13. the scientist is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
14. the librarian is on the left or right of the bartender##3
15. the project-manager is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Color         | ivory | blood-red    | mauve | emerald       |
| Job           | librarian | bartender  | scientist   | project-manager |
