The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, marigold, begonia
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, milk, cola
 1. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking milk and the person eating blueberry##2
 2. the nurse is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the nurse##1
 4. the security-guard is in an even position##4
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 9. the entrepreneur is the person eating watermelon##1
10. the person eating blueberry is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching action movies##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
14. the person eating blueberry is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| Food          | watermelon   | banana        | pepper      | blueberry      |
