 2. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the teacher is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the analyst is the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
14. the analyst is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

