 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the ranch-style house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who likes apricot and the art-deco house##2
 9. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
11. the art-deco house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the designer##3
13. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
