.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, broccoli, eggplant, grapes
There are 4 different nationalities: american, pakistani, spanish, egyptian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, horror, western
City: london, berlin, new-york, liverpool
 1. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 2. the spanish is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person traveling to london is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person traveling to berlin and the spanish##2
 7. the person drinking tea is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
10. the american is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person eating broccoli is the spanish##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea      | mirinda      | lemonade |
| Food          | artichoke | eggplant | grapes       | broccoli |
| Nationality         | american   | egyptian   | pakistani | spanish  |
