.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, traveling
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, brown, fuchsia, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting, baseball, handball
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goldfish, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the bike is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes blood-red##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who likes brown##2
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
13. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
14. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing       | drawing    | traveling | hiking     |
| Color           | blood-red | fuchsia  | brown  | blue       |
| Sport   | baseball         | surfing        | handball     | weightlifting |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | goldfish   | cat       | lizard     |
| Transport     | taxi          | snowmobile | bike      | skateboard |

